title: A.S. Tiare Anani
text: Association Sportive Tiare Anani is a <a href="association%20football">football</a> club from <a href="Pao%20Pao">Pao Pao</a>, <a href="Moorea">Moorea</a>, <a href="French%20Polynesia">French Polynesia</a>. It currently competes in the <a href="Ligue%202%20Moorea">Ligue 2 Moorea</a>,the regional league of <a href="Moorea">Moorea</a>.
